UseAlignedGridLevels: Disable to help break the pattern caused by world partition promotion of actors to upper grid levels that are always aligned on child levels.
SnapNonAlignedGridLevelsToLowerLevels: Disable to avoid snapping higher levels cells to child cells. Only used when bUseAlignedGridLevels is false.
PlaceSmallActorsUsingLocation: Enable to place actors smaller than a cell size into their corresponding cell using their location instead of their bounding box.
PlacePartitionActorsUsingLocation: Enable to place partitioned actors into their corresponding cell using their location instead of their bounding box.
bEnableZCulling: Whether this hash enables Z culling.
